.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, january, june
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, snowmobile, motorbike
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, grey, blue
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the owner of the pony is the british##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in february##2
 5. the dutch is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 7. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Birthday      | february   | june    | january         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Transport   | taxi  | motorbike  | snowmobile     |
| Color   | blue       | grey      | fuchsia         |
| Nationality   | dutch      | british   | australian    |
| Pet           | dog        | pony      | horse         |
| Sport         | water-polo | baseball  | weightlifting |

