 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is the person playing bridge##1
 8. the musician is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the person drinking milk is between the musician and the social-worker##2
10. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1

