 3. the polish is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the futuristic house##1
 5. the prince-smoker is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 7. the blend-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in august and the american##2
 8. the cottage house is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the futuristic house is the prince-smoker##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the prince-smoker is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | august | may      | november      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| House   | palace | cottage  | futuristic |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | polish     | american |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Sport         | handball    | water-polo | soccer   |
| Cigar     | chaman        | blend        | prince   |

