.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, electronic, dubstep
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daisy, amaryllis
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, hiking, singing
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, ambientsy, mystery
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, water-polo
City: rome, london, marseilles
1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the musician##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the dressmaker##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching epic movies and the manager##2
5. the person who growsamaryllis is between the musician and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
8. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
9. the person watching ambientsy movies is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
