.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, tea
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, spinach, zucchini
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, animation, epic
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, french, italian
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, rabbit
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, swisher, alhambra
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, lily, bellflower
1. the person drinking milk is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is between the person drinking tea and the owner of the rabbit##2
4. the canadian is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
6. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
7. the person watching animation movies is the person eating broccoli##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the french is between the person eating broccoli and the person who growsiris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | milk       | tea      |
| Food          | broccoli   | zucchini   | spinach  |
| Movie-Genre           | animation  | superhero | epic    |
| Nationality   | canadian   | french     | italian  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | dog        | hedgehog |
| Cigar         | swisher | tiparillo   | alhambra  |
| Flower     | lily    | bellflower     | iris      |

 